<i>Posted by Ulaa on 06-13-2001 04:48 AM:</i>

<p><b> Nerfs</b></p>

<p>Guys I in no way intended any negativity towards the Shaman Class or the Achievement of Nixx from my posting.<br />
<br />
<blockquote><FONT face="arial,helvetica" size="1" color="#FFFFFF">quote:</font><hr>You knobs.. he did it with endless charge items.. necro's are nerfed because their natural skills are unbalanced.. had Nixx did this with regular ol' mana and shaman spells<hr></blockquote> <br />
<br />
We werent necessarily Nerfed because of what we are intrinsically capable of. We got bashed with the nerf stick so many times because of class envy. So many people posted that it "wasnt fair" that necros could do this that and the other thing that eventually Verant started to seriously look at us.<br />
<br />
Wont it be fun for you when every Warrior/Enchanter/Cleric/Druid/Bard etc etc starts screaming "Look at what the shaman can do!, they can SOLO dragons!". Then when Verant starts the Nerfing you will wish you had shut up. (The entire Necro community certainly wishes we hadnt been so arrogant at times) <br />
<br />
