Id like to put it this way for those of you who are still reading this. It has long been a tenent of the Necro community that we arent such good soloists simply because we are powerful, we are also good soloists because WE KNOW OUR CLASS. Like the Shaman the Necro in a group is a mostly a support class, like the shamn the Necro will only reach High level if he/she KNOWS what they are doing, how their spells work and how to use them effectively.<br />
<br />
