<p><b> </b></p>

<p>Reasons necros were nerfed....<br />
<br />
Necros could literally park their pet in places and FD.  They would go to bed while their pets got them exp all night.  I've seen this happen and I have a friend that has done this.  He would park his pet inbetween the two guards outside of Oggok and go to bed.  When he woke in the morning he had quite a bit of exp.<br />
<br />
Verant tried to change this by making FD a short duration spell.  This did not work.  They had to do something about that incredible pet.  Necros could stick two rust daggers in their pet's hands and it would be like giving him Wonderous Rapidity.<br />
<br />
I remember the days when I would take a full group to camp the fort in LG and one necro would spoil the fun by camping the entire place.  This stuff happened.<br />
<br />
What this inovative shaman did was nothing at all like what necros could and would do.  <br />
