<p><b> Concerning Lodizal</b></p>

<p>If you want Lodizal's shell, I suggest you camp him and have 1-2 other people with you to kill him. Lodizal is cake, I camped him in the first few weeks of June and killed him 3 times. I got myself a shield (makes 2 since I had one already), Belt of the Great turtle, and an eyepatch for my level 39 SK, and silly boots. The Cleric got 2 lodizal shields and boots, and the monk got 1 lodizal shield, a club. He had an eyepatch already so that was the only reason my SK looted it <img src="images/smilies/biggrin.gif" border="0" alt=""> <br />
