<br />
A Necro on my server was able to solo a Jugg(hits:~170) but thats rather easy compared to Yeldema. I high doubt a necro could take Yeldema's 20k or so hp. I had a log of it but forgot to do at the start of the fight. Necro wouldn't be able to heal his pet for the rounds of double 219. Also Yeld rampages once in a while (killed my pet and I didn't even realize it, was on me the whole time) Buffed my pet with focus and it still died by ONLY rampages. It died at 30% so had to finish off Yeld with only bracer/epic <br />
